About VentureBeat
GamesBeat covers stories about the evolving video game industry, from disruptive social game companies such as Zynga and CrowdStar, to the established giants such as Electronic Arts, Activision Blizzard, Microsoft, Sony, and Nintendo. We cover the companies and trends that matter to entrepreneurs, executives and investors.
